/**********************************************************************************************
Name  : [logi].[pr_ringo_AdviserComplaintTotals]
Author      : S Inglis
Date  : 26/11/2015

Purpose     : This report is used for Project Ringo. The recipients are:
                  1) T&C Team

              The report name is "AdviserComplaintTotals" and is found on the "Ringo MI" 
              menu. This report displays the total number of complaints an adviser has 
			  against them in a rolling 12 months, the number of which are upheld and 
			  justified and the number of which are upheld and unjustified



              The security groups associated with is report are:
              1) 
              2)  

              Execute as follows:
              exec [logi].[pr_logi_AdviserComplaintTotals] 30, 'ptl91371'

AMENDMENT HISTORY
