Purpose     : This report is used for Project Ringo. The recipients are:
                  1) T&C Team

              The report name is "Deep Span Event Detail" and is found on the "BQM MI" 
              menu. This report displays: 
              - A list of Late Events (Report & Review)



              The security groups associated with is report are:
              1) 
              2)  

              Execute as follows:
              exec [logi].[pr_ringoDeepSpanEventDetail] 'ptl91371', 'SQL','View All'

