AS 


set nocount on
/**********************************************************************************************
Name  : [logi].[pr_ringo_FirmMCOBTrigger]
Author      : S Inglis
Date  : 31/10/2017

Purpose     : This report is used for Project Ringo. The recipients are:
                  1) T&C Team

              The report name is "Firm MCOB Triggers" and is found on the "BQM MI" 
              menu. This report displays: 
              - Mortgage Triggers for the Firm alongside details of the national average.
              This stored procedure replaced pr_ringo_MOCBBusMixFirm



      The security groups associated with is report are:
      1) 
      2)  

