Execute as follows:
exec [logi].[pr_ringo_MCOBTriggersDeepSpan] 'ptl91371',@AQMUID,Null,Null,Null,'Null','Management'

AMENDMENT HISTORY
=================
Date        Author            Description
----        ------            -----------

***********************************************************************************************/


/****************************************************************************

      Initialisation                                                                                              
                                                                                                            
****************************************************************************/



