 Description:   This proc transfers the MCOBS/ICOB Quality Leagues data from the staging table 
				loaded by SSIS to the main table.
				
				Note: Quality Leagues are only updated quarterly
				
				It is called as follows:

				exec [TandC].[Pr_QLS_MCOBICOB_Insert]
													
Amendment History								
